thread.title: T.J. Fisher

author: T.J. Fisher
title: T.J. Fisher
text: I just ordered my first set of workout clothes from here and I am super excited! Working out should be fun and I think looking cute while you do, at least for me, makes it all the more motivating. I love the VIP outline and I'm glad that I don't lose any money each month, that everything is credited to my account and I can use it whenever. Plus, I can cancel anytime (though it won't be for a while ;) ).
